data.description: Hard to find brick ranch-basement home sitting on 1.33 acres in Matthews! Hardwood in all 4 bedrooms, family room and living room. Generous sized bedrooms. Large deck (composite deck boards) off of the sunroom overlooks huge backyard. Over 2400 square feet of living area and a huge 1453 square foot basement. Two car garage with lots of storage space. Also, a 2-car covered carport area. No HOA dues. Top rated schools. Shed in back does not convey.
